    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a reliable and comfortable driving experience. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts precisely, and all essential mechanical systems are in great working order. While there may be minor cosmetic wear consistent with regular use, the interior is clean and the exterior retains a polished look. This is a solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable car that is ready for the road.",
